node.text:
DILLA 21- Fell first moto & broke off my rear brake pedal came from the back to 15th. Moto 2 came away with an 8th, Not great woulda been nice to get a couple good finishes but that’s racing. Also massive shout out to the fans you guys rock supporting me when I’m not at my best! 🤜🏽🤛🏽 See ya in Maryland💪🏽📈
.
.
